title: Strictly Come Dancing: Peter Andre will transform into Jack Sparrow for Movie Week - Strictly Come Dancing Reality TV -
text: Peter Andre will be donning the eyeliner on Saturday for Strictly Come Dancing, when he'll transform into Jack Sparrow for Movie Week.The 'Mysterious Girl' singer isn't sure what he'll be dancing yet, but it's set to take on a Pirates of the Caribbean theme. © BBC / Ray Burmiston Strictly Come Dancing 2015 winner: We rank the celebrities' chances of topping BBC One's dance-off"All I know is who I'm going to be. I'm very, very excited because I'm going to be Jack Sparrow from Pirates of the Caribbean and I cannot wait," Andre exclusively told Digital Spy."I'm so excited about it that I just want to give it my all. It's going to be good fun," he added. © Rex Features / W. Disney/Everett Andre and his dancing partner Janette Manrara scored 30 on Saturday's show with their quickstep to 'Valerie'.Following the weekend shows, former pro James Jordan suggested that Andre might be enjoying an unfair advantage over other contestants.Watch Peter and Janette quickstepping to 'Valerie' below:
